OL,3,CNew 10m sports village could open
OL,4,Cwithin the next two years
OL,6,FA new 10m sports village in West
OL,7,FCumbria could open within the next two
OL,8,Fyears.
OL,10,FThe development includes a stadium for
OL,11,FWorkington Reds and Workington Town
OL,12,FLeague club which will be built on the
OL,13,Fexisting Borough Park site.
OL,15,FThose behind the scheme say the
OL,16,Fstadium will hold 3,700 sitting and
OL,17,Fstanding spectators. Floodlights and
OL,18,Fparking facilities will also be
OL,19,Fadjusted to fit the facility.
