OL,3,CNew 10m sports village could open
OL,4,Cwithin the next two years
OL,6,FBoth Workington AFC and Workington
OL,7,FRLFC will have the opportunity to hold
OL,8,Fengagement events over the summer.
OL,10,FWith a planning application set to be
OL,11,Fsubmitted by the end of July 2025, its
OL,12,Fexpected construction work will begin
OL,13,Fin early 2026, finishing within 18
OL,14,Fmonths.
OL,16,FThe existing pitch will also be
OL,17,Freplaced with a 3G pitch suitable for
OL,18,Fboth football and rugby.
