OL,6,FDave Bowden, spokesman for Cumberland
OL,7,FSports Village, said: "We're pleased
OL,8,Fto be part of such positive progress
OL,9,Fon the Cumberland Sports Village
OL,10,Fproject.
OL,12,F"It's a project built on partnership
OL,13,Fand shared vision and we're excited by
OL,14,Fthe potential it holds to create
OL,15,Flasting benefits for Workington AFC,
OL,16,FWorkington Town RLFC, and the whole
OL,17,Fcommunity.
