OL,6,FA spokesperson from Workington AFC
OL,7,Fsaid: "The proposed development will
OL,8,Fprovide a modern, high-quality
OL,9,Ffacility to support first-team
OL,10,Fperformance, youth development, and
OL,11,Fthe ongoing delivery of our club's
OL,12,Fcommunity programmes across West
OL,13,FCumbria.
OL,15,F"It also presents valuable commercial
OL,16,Fopportunities to help secure long-term
OL,17,Fsustainability. The Board of
OL,18,FWorkington AFC looks forward to help
OL,19,Fmake these plans a reality for our
OL,20,Fclub and community."
